      "text": "DAVIS, Stanley M., 1990. [[Future Perfect]]. In: EVANS, Paul, DOZ, Yves and LAURENT, André (eds.), Human Resource Management in International Firms: Change, Globalization, Innovation. London: Palgrave Macmillan UK. p. 18–28. ISBN 978-1-349-11255-5, p. 23."
