      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "e4c3f4ab3952d201",
      "text": "WEICK, Karl E., 1988. Future Perfect. Academy of Management Perspectives. November 1988. Vol. 2, no. 4, p. 333–334. DOI 10.5465/ame.1988.4274780. \n"
