    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "cdedac10afc6f9f3",
      "text": "Schutz borrows a term from grammar in order to express this complex situation. He says that we picture the goal of the action \"in the future perfect tense\" (modo futuri exacti)."
